    {"id":"c21b","type":"text","x":640,"y":380,"width":480,"height":590,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":203,"version":1,"versionNonce":203,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"text":"① TRIGGER\nRegular on WhatsApp at 18:52:\n\"Move our 8 tonight 19:30 → 20:00?\nTrain delay.\"\n\n② AGENT DETECTS\nReservation change · 30min shift\nConflicts with Kaiser 20:00/6\nConfidence 44% · Rec: modify\n(suggests 20:15)\n\n③ OWNER SEES (glanceable card)\n\"Ricci 8pax — move to 20:00?\n🔴 Conflicts Kaiser 20:00/6\nAgent suggests 20:15\"\n🎙 \"Make it nine fifteen\"\n\n④ OWNER DECIDES\nHands in flour. Phone to ear:\n\"20:15, but put them at table 12.\"\nVoice → whisper slot.\n\n⑤ AGENT RESUMES\n\"Moved to 20:15, table 12 (bit\nquieter, near the window).\nSee you soon!\"\n\n⑥ OUTCOME\nNo conflict. Kaiser unaware.\nLuca's screen time: 3 seconds.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"① TRIGGER\nRegular on WhatsApp at 18:52:\n\"Move our 8 tonight 19:30 → 20:00?\nTrain delay.\"\n\n② AGENT DETECTS\nReservation change · 30min shift\nConflicts with Kaiser 20:00/6\nConfidence 44% · Rec: modify\n(suggests 20:15)\n\n③ OWNER SEES (glanceable card)\n\"Ricci 8pax — move to 20:00?\n🔴 Conflicts Kaiser 20:00/6\nAgent suggests 20:15\"\n🎙 \"Make it nine fifteen\"\n\n④ OWNER DECIDES\nHands in flour. Phone to ear:\n\"20:15, but put them at table 12.\"\nVoice → whisper slot.\n\n⑤ AGENT RESUMES\n\"Moved to 20:15, table 12 (bit\nquieter, near the window).\nSee you soon!\"\n\n⑥ OUTCOME\nNo conflict. Kaiser unaware.\nLuca's screen time: 3 seconds.","lineHeight":1.25,"baseline":12},

