    {"id":"c23b","type":"text","x":640,"y":1840,"width":480,"height":590,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":223,"version":1,"versionNonce":223,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"text":"① TRIGGER\nSystem event, 07:40:\nWeekly produce auto-draft\nTomatoes +38% w/w\n\n② AGENT DETECTS\nRecurring action · over ceiling\n(€1,240 vs €900 usual)\nConfidence 51% · Rec: hold\n\n③ OWNER SEES (still in bed)\n\"Produce order ready\n⚠️ €1,240 · +38% tomatoes\nTap to see basket ▸\"\n[Send] [Halve tomatoes]\n[Skip tomatoes] [Call supplier]\n\n④ OWNER DECIDES\nTaps Skip tomatoes.\nAdds reason: \"Will use tinned\nfor the bolognese special.\"\n\n⑤ AGENT RESUMES\n→ Supplier API: order minus tomatoes\n→ Menu: promote bolognese\n→ Head chef on WhatsApp:\n\"Bolognese special tomorrow —\ntinned, tomatoes skipped.\"\n\n⑥ OUTCOME\n€280 saved · no waste · chef\nnot ambushed. Reason becomes\ntraining data for next spike.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"① TRIGGER\nSystem event, 07:40:\nWeekly produce auto-draft\nTomatoes +38% w/w\n\n② AGENT DETECTS\nRecurring action · over ceiling\n(€1,240 vs €900 usual)\nConfidence 51% · Rec: hold\n\n③ OWNER SEES (still in bed)\n\"Produce order ready\n⚠️ €1,240 · +38% tomatoes\nTap to see basket ▸\"\n[Send] [Halve tomatoes]\n[Skip tomatoes] [Call supplier]\n\n④ OWNER DECIDES\nTaps Skip tomatoes.\nAdds reason: \"Will use tinned\nfor the bolognese special.\"\n\n⑤ AGENT RESUMES\n→ Supplier API: order minus tomatoes\n→ Menu: promote bolognese\n→ Head chef on WhatsApp:\n\"Bolognese special tomorrow —\ntinned, tomatoes skipped.\"\n\n⑥ OUTCOME\n€280 saved · no waste · chef\nnot ambushed. Reason becomes\ntraining data for next spike.","lineHeight":1.25,"baseline":12},

