    {"id":"c24t","type":"text","x":640,"y":2515,"width":480,"height":50,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":242,"version":1,"versionNonce":242,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"text":"2.4  🐟 Fish Supplier Fails Mid-Day\n🎯 CONSTRAIN + ✏️ MODIFY (custom)","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"2.4  🐟 Fish Supplier Fails Mid-Day\n🎯 CONSTRAIN + ✏️ MODIFY (custom)","lineHeight":1.25,"baseline":14},
    {"id":"c24b","type":"text","x":640,"y":2590,"width":480,"height":670,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":243,"version":1,"versionNonce":243,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"text":"① TRIGGER\nInventory agent placed tonight's\nfish order 48h ago with Vendor 1\n(inside weekly budget).\n14:20 — 4h before service —\nVendor 1 flagged \"not dispatched.\"\nAgent pings Vendors 2 & 3 for\npriority quotes. V2 replies in 6min.\n\n② AGENT DETECTS\nSupply-chain failure · 38 covers\nbooked · V2 quote +22% over budget\nV3 unquoted · risk escalates /15min\nConfidence 58% · Rec: accept V2,\nflag overrun.\n\n③ OWNER SEES (lock screen, 14:26)\n🐟 \"Fish for tonight — V1 won't deliver\nV2 can: +€180 over budget (+22%)\nV3: quote pending\n38 covers · service 18:30\"\n[Accept V2] [Wait for V3]\n[Custom…] [Give me V2's contact]\n\n④ OWNER DECIDES\nTaps Custom…, dictates while plating:\n\"Take V2, but only tonight's amount —\nnot the full week.\"\n\"If V3 cheaper within 20min, swap;\notherwise lock V2.\"\nVariance updates: +€95 (+12%).\n20-min fallback timer starts.\n\n⑤ AGENT RESUMES\n→ V2: places partial order, window\n  17:00–17:30, requests delivery note\n→ V3: chased with 20-min deadline\n→ Head chef WA: \"Fish from V2 tonight\n  only, 17:00–17:30. Menu unchanged.\"\n→ Accounting: flags +€95 with reason\n→ V1 (polite, firm): \"You didn't deliver.\n  Sourced elsewhere. Confirm won't\n  repeat, or we'll review the contract.\"\n\n⑥ OUTCOME\nService on time · no cancellations\n€95 overrun absorbed knowingly\nV1 escalation paper-trail started\nV3 missed window, V2 locked.\nLearning: \"Luca prefers partial\n/tonight-only over full replacement\nwhen V1 fails.\" → Next time, partial\nbecomes the pre-selected default.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"① TRIGGER\nInventory agent placed tonight's\nfish order 48h ago with Vendor 1\n(inside weekly budget).\n14:20 — 4h before service —\nVendor 1 flagged \"not dispatched.\"\nAgent pings Vendors 2 & 3 for\npriority quotes. V2 replies in 6min.\n\n② AGENT DETECTS\nSupply-chain failure · 38 covers\nbooked · V2 quote +22% over budget\nV3 unquoted · risk escalates /15min\nConfidence 58% · Rec: accept V2,\nflag overrun.\n\n③ OWNER SEES (lock screen, 14:26)\n🐟 \"Fish for tonight — V1 won't deliver\nV2 can: +€180 over budget (+22%)\nV3: quote pending\n38 covers · service 18:30\"\n[Accept V2] [Wait for V3]\n[Custom…] [Give me V2's contact]\n\n④ OWNER DECIDES\nTaps Custom…, dictates while plating:\n\"Take V2, but only tonight's amount —\nnot the full week.\"\n\"If V3 cheaper within 20min, swap;\notherwise lock V2.\"\nVariance updates: +€95 (+12%).\n20-min fallback timer starts.\n\n⑤ AGENT RESUMES\n→ V2: places partial order, window\n  17:00–17:30, requests delivery note\n→ V3: chased with 20-min deadline\n→ Head chef WA: \"Fish from V2 tonight\n  only, 17:00–17:30. Menu unchanged.\"\n→ Accounting: flags +€95 with reason\n→ V1 (polite, firm): \"You didn't deliver.\n  Sourced elsewhere. Confirm won't\n  repeat, or we'll review the contract.\"\n\n⑥ OUTCOME\nService on time · no cancellations\n€95 overrun absorbed knowingly\nV1 escalation paper-trail started\nV3 missed window, V2 locked.\nLearning: \"Luca prefers partial\n/tonight-only over full replacement\nwhen V1 fails.\" → Next time, partial\nbecomes the pre-selected default.","lineHeight":1.25,"baseline":12},

    {"id":"ftr","type":"text","x":80,"y":3320,"width":1600,"height":30,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#495057","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":999,"version":1,"versionNonce":999,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":18,"fontFamily":1,"text":"Every card follows the same 6-step shape: Trigger → Agent detects → Owner sees → Owner decides → Agent resumes → Outcome","textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Every card follows the same 6-step shape: Trigger → Agent detects → Owner sees → Owner decides → Agent resumes → Outcome","lineHeight":1.25,"baseline":18}
